				The Water Pet Reagains Health the Fastest and also has a Attack Spell.   The Earth Elemental Might Have More HP, but after a Hard battle you will be out of Mana to heal him, So you have to Med Up, then Heal Him, and then med again, which is really Time Consuming.   While With the Water, before you Have your Mana back, it will be at 100% and Ready to Attack.   I dont know how many times that has Saved me, since monsters dont care if you are Medding, they will attack you, and Your Water Pet will have Alot more HP back from the Previous Fight than the Earth Elemental and be able to let you med Longer for Spells, or Zone before it Dies and you get Killed.
